Description: MOD Web UI — web-based pedalboard interface for pi-Stomp
 MOD UI is a web-based interface for managing pedalboards on MOD
 devices. This build runs in a Python 3.11 venv (required by
 tornado==4.3) and is configured for pi-Stomp.
